Program: Great Lives
Title: Bette Davis
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00gd3f0
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 28 Apr 2017
Series of biographical discussions with Matthew Parris. Actress Tracy-Ann Oberman champions the life of Hollywood actress Bette Davis. Joining the discussion is Davis expert Robyn Karney who explores her complex character and achievements.